      "grammarNotes": "### 'Dám si' — ordering food\n\nCzechs use **Dám si** (I'll give myself) to order food:\n- `Dám si pivo.` — I'll have a beer.\n- `Dám si guláš.` — I'll have goulash.\n\nIt's more natural than saying 'Chci' (I want), which can sound demanding."
